  }), "Location\xA01326"), ")"), mdx("h3", null, "New highlights added November 2nd, 2020 at 9:21 AM"), mdx("p", null, "\u201CWe use the term ego depletion to refer to a temporary reduction in the self\u2019s capacity or willingness to engage in volitional action (including controlling the environment, controlling the self, making choices, and initiating action) caused by prior exercise of volition.\u201D (", mdx("a", _extends({
