  }, {
    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=1454"
  }), "Location\xA01454"), ")"), mdx("p", null, "Developing arguments and ideas bottom-up instead of top-down is the first and most important step to opening ourselves up for insight. (", mdx("a", _extends({
    parentName: "p"
  }, {
    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=1490"
