  }, {
    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=1503"
  }), "Location\xA01503"), ")"), mdx("p", null, "Yes, we have to be selective, but not in terms of pros and cons, but in terms of relevant or irrelevant. (", mdx("a", _extends({
