    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=1673"
  }), "Location\xA01673"), ")"), mdx("p", null, "The brain, as Kahneman writes, is \u201Ca machine for jumping to conclusions\u201D (", mdx("a", _extends({
