  }, {
    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=1993"
  }), "Location\xA01993"), ")"), mdx("p", null, "The way people choose their keywords shows clearly if they think like an archivist or a writer. Do they wonder where to store a note or how to retrieve it? The archivist asks: Which keyword is the most fitting? A writer asks: In which circumstances will I want to stumble upon this note, even if I forget about it? It is a crucial difference. (", mdx("a", _extends({
