    "href": "https://readwise.io/to_kindle?action=open&asin=B06WVYW33Y&location=2403"
  }), "Location\xA02403"), ")"), mdx("p", null, "\u201CRemember the lesson: \u2018An idea or a fact is not worth more merely because it is easily available to you.\u2019\u201D (Charles T. Munger) (", mdx("a", _extends({
    parentName: "p"
  }, {
